  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">School for Vulnerable Children  in Liberia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through the construction of a school in Clay-Ashland in Liberia, we will provide children from poor, disadvantaged communities with access to high-quality, affordable education. Our school will be the first in Clay-Ashland and will focus on children aged 5 to 14 years old. This will be a holistic facility that will also include a cafeteria, providing nutritious food to children, and a library that gives children access to a variety of books to promote a reading culture.</narrative>
  </description>
